VALUES
	(6,'',2,2,0,'about-airpapr','cat_name_show_en','cat_description_en','about-airpapr','airpapr','18.01.11','Patrick','airpapr','<p><big>airpapr Content Management System</big></p>\r\n<div class=\"wp-caption alignleft\" style=\"width: 180px;\" _mce_style=\"width: 180px;\"><a class=\"pic-link\" rel=\"airpapr-screenshots\" href=\"/upload-pics/airpapr-login.png\" _mce_href=\"upload-pics/airpapr-login.png\"><img class=\"size-full\" title=\"koi\" src=\"/img/zc/1/w/170/h/142/airpapr-login.png\" _mce_src=\"img/zc/1/w/170/h/142/airpapr-login.png\" alt=\"Airpapr login window\" height=\"142\" width=\"170\"></a>\r\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">airpapr login window</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>airpapr is a modern, easy to use, lightweight and flexible content management system which is built on PHP and MySQL. airpapr is a full featured content management system which allows users to create complex and large websites. airpapr features, among other things, a unlimited number of subcategories and multi-language support. At the same time airpapr is just as easy to use as Wordpress or any other blogging software. If you know how to use a word processor program, you can easily publish websites with airpapr. airpapr\'s innovative template engine also gives designer the full control over the design of a site, without having to write a single line of PHP code.</p>\r\n<p><big>Open Source</big></p>\r\n<p>We plan to release airpapr as open source software under the <a href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\" _mce_href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\">GNU General Public License</a>. This means you can use airpapr freely for anything from a personal to a commercial website. airpapr is at the moment in beta status, all functions finished and at the moment we are fixing the last bugs. As usual, we are going to release airpapr when it\'s done, but we guesstimate that we will be able to release airpapr in then next few months from now.</p>\r\n<p><big>Designer Freedom</big></p>\r\n<div class=\"wp-caption alignright\" style=\"width: 180px;\" _mce_style=\"width: 180px;\"><a class=\"pic-link\" rel=\"airpapr-screenshots\" href=\"/upload-pics/airpapr-old-browser-warning.png\" _mce_href=\"upload-pics/airpapr-old-browser-warning.png\"><img class=\"size-full\" title=\"koi\" src=\"/img/zc/1/w/170/h/142/airpapr-old-browser-warning.png\" _mce_src=\"img/zc/1/w/170/h/142/airpapr-old-browser-warning.png\" alt=\"Old browser Warning message\" height=\"142\" width=\"170\"></a>\r\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Old browser Warning message</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>airpapr gives web designer who know HTML, CSS &amp; JavaScript the full control over the design of  a site, without having to know or write a single line of PHP code. airpapr uses a advanced, easy to use template engine, with it\'s own easy to learn API, which is similar to the HTML syntax. For somebody how already knows HTML, the learning curve is nearly non existent. airpapr also offers advanced layout features, for example the ability to detect mobile devices and use a mobile optimized templates or the ability to detect older browsers (such as IE6) and warn the visitor that it may come to display errors if you want to use bleeding edge technologies like CSS 3 and HTML 5.</p>\r\n<p><em>Here you can see a typical article block written with the airpapr</em><em> templating API:</em></p>\r\n<pre class=\"brush: xml; toolbar: false;\">&lt;div class=\"post\"&gt;\r\n	&lt;h2&gt;&lt;airpapr-article-title&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=\"post-date\"&gt;&lt;airpapr-article-date&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=\"postauthor\"&gt;&lt;airpapr-user&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=\"postcategory\"&gt;&lt;airpapr-article-title&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;&lt;airpapr-article-date&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;!-- inserts a small box with the ui to delete or edit the article --&gt;\r\n	&lt;airpapr-cms-onpage-editbox&gt;\r\n	&lt;!-- insets images associated to the article, with class, linked, width, height and zoom crop option --&gt;\r\n	&lt;airpapr-article-img class=\"size-full\" view=\"single\" width=\"170\" height=\"142\" zc=\"1\"&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=\"caption-text\"&gt;&lt;airpapr-article-title&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;airpapr-article-text&gt;\r\n	&lt;a href=\"&lt;airpapr-link&gt;\"&gt;More...&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n<p><big>Lightweight and resource-efficient</big></p>\r\n<p>In it\'s current development status airpapr is just 1,3MB small and only needs a server with <span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\" _mce_style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">PHP 4</span> <a _mce_href=\"/en/page/php-5-oop-and-pdo\" href=\"/en/page/php-5-oop-and-pdo\">PHP 5.1</a> and MySQL 4 to run smoothly. Therefor airpapr can run on (nearly) any web hosting server.</p>\r\n<p><big>Flexible and powerful - easy to use</big></p>\r\n<div class=\"wp-caption alignleft\" style=\"width: 180px;\" _mce_style=\"width: 180px;\"><a class=\"pic-link\" rel=\"airpapr-screenshots\" href=\"/upload-pics/airpapr-new-article-edit.png\" _mce_href=\"upload-pics/airpapr-new-article-edit.png\"><img class=\"size-full\" title=\"koi\" src=\"/img/zc/1/w/170/h/142/airpapr-new-article-edit.png\" _mce_src=\"img/zc/1/w/170/h/142/airpapr-new-article-edit.png\" alt=\"Airpapr article window\" height=\"142\" width=\"170\"></a>\r\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">airpapr article window</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>airpapr is a full featured content management system, but at the same time features a very user friendly interface. Anyone how knows how to use a word processing program is able use airpapr. airpapr offers a innovative user interface, which isn\'t separated into a front- and back end (like Wordpress or Typo 3), but as soon as you log in to airpapr, every page is editable like a open word document. You can directly create new pages, edit existing ones or delete pages right form the page. A task bar, which you are familiar with form your OS, is used as the main control element. All controls that you need to mange your site are located there.</p>\r\n<p><big>Safety built in</big></p>\r\n<p>airpapr was built form the ground up with security in mined. Therefor is airpapr is developed to the highest PHP security standard and also offers advanced security features like the custom template system, that runs completely without any PHP code, thereby eliminating the risk of comprising the security of your website by installing third party templates.</p>\r\n<p><big>Standard compliant - HTML 5</big></p>\r\n<div class=\"wp-caption alignright\" style=\"width: 180px;\" _mce_style=\"width: 180px;\"><a class=\"pic-link\" rel=\"airpapr-screenshots\" href=\"/upload-pics/airpapr-user-management.png\" _mce_href=\"upload-pics/airpapr-user-management.png\"><img class=\"size-full\" title=\"koi\" src=\"/img/zc/1/w/170/h/142/airpapr-user-management.png\" _mce_src=\"img/zc/1/w/170/h/142/airpapr-user-management.png\" alt=\"Airpapr settings window\" height=\"142\" width=\"170\"></a>\r\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">airpapr settings window</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Web standards are important to ensure that the web is accessible for all internet users. Companies like Apple and Google have acknowledged the importance of web standards like HTML 5 and are actively supporting them. airpapr creates 100% W3C Standard compliant code (HTML and CSS) which is also HTML 5 ready. With future versions of airpapr we will also add native HTML 5 functions to airpapr, such as HTML 5 video and audio.</p>\r\n<p><big>Mobile optimized websites</big></p>\r\n<p>airpapr automatically recognizes if a website is view form a hand held device like an iPhone or Android smart phone and can deliver a custom mobile template for your website without having to write any PHP code.</p>','<p><big>airpapr Content Management System</big></p>\n\n<p><div class=\"wp-caption alignleft\" style=\"width: 180px;\" _mce_style=\"width: 180px;\"><a class=\"pic-link\" rel=\"airpapr-screenshots\" href=\"/upload-pics/airpapr-login.png\" _mce_href=\"upload-pics/airpapr-login.png\"><img class=\"size-full\" ti