alignright\" style=\"width: 180px;\" _mce_style=\"width: 180px;\"><a class=\"pic-link\" rel=\"airpapr-screenshots\" href=\"/upload-pics/airpapr-user-management.png\" _mce_href=\"upload-pics/airpapr-user-management.png\"><img class=\"size-full\" title=\"koi\" src=\"/img/zc/1/w/170/h/142/airpapr-user-management.png\" _mce_src=\"img/zc/1/w/170/h/142/airpapr-user-management.png\" alt=\"Airpapr settings window\" height=\"142\" width=\"170\"></a>\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">airpapr settings window</p>\n</div>\n<p>Web standards are important to ensure that the web is accessible for all internet users. Companies like Apple and Google have acknowledged the importance of web standards like HTML 5 and are actively supporting them. airpapr creates 100% W3C Standard compliant code (HTML and CSS) which is also HTML 5 ready. With future versions of airpapr we will also add native HTML 5 functions to airpapr, such as HTML 5 video and audio.</p>\n<p><big>Mobile optimized websites</big></p>\n<p>airpapr automatically recognizes if a website is view form a hand held device like an iPhone or Android smart phone and can deliver a custom mobile template for your website without having to write any PHP code.</p></p>\n','','','','','',1),
