	(82,'news',1,1,0,'airpapr-beta-release','cat_name_show_en','cat_description_en','airpapr-beta-release','airpapr beta release','25.04.11','Patrick','airpapr beta release','<p>Hello and welcome back to yet an other very special airpapr update. Today we have a rather big announcement, the  beta release of airpapr to the public! As promised we are releasing airpapr as open source software to under the <a href=\\\"http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\\\">GNU GPL v3</a> license. You can <a href=\\\"http://blog.airpapr.com/en/page/download\\\">download the beta right here</a>, on our github page.</p>\r\n<p>Befor you start downloading the airpapr beta, you may want to check out the <a href=\\\"http://blog.airpapr.com/en/page/documentation\\\">documentation</a>. On the same page you can also find the template API and file structure reference. In the very near future we are planning on releasing some in-depth tutorials and how-to on how to set up and run airpapr on your server and also on how to write your own airpapr templates.</p>\r\n<p>If you have any questions or feedback, we would <a href=\\\"http://blog.airpapr.com/en/contact\\\">love to here from you</a>! Also, if you found any bugs or have any problems with airpapr, it would be great if you could drop a short <a href=\\\"https://github.com/airpapr/airpapr/issues\\\">issue report</a> on our github page.</p>\r\n<p>As you may also have noticed, we have decided to drop the German language support from the airpapr website. It was just not reasonable to take the extra time to translate every article into German, for a very small audience. Inserted we are focusing on writing the documentation of airpapr and the production of tutorials.</p>','<p>Hello and welcome back to yet an other very special airpapr update. Today we have a rather big announcement, the  beta release of airpapr to the public! As promised we are releasing airpapr as open source software to under the <a href=\\\"http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\\\">GNU GPL v3</a> license. You can <a href=\\\"http://blog.airpapr.com/en/page/download\\\">download the beta right here</a>, on our github page.</p>\n\n<p><p>Befor you start downloading the airpapr beta, you may want to check out the <a href=\\\"http://blog.airpapr.com/en/page/documentation\\\">documentation</a>. On the same page you can also find the template API and file structure reference. In the very near future we are planning on releasing some in-depth tutorials and how-to on how to set up and run airpapr on your server and also on how to write your own airpapr templates.</p>\n<p>If you have any questions or feedback, we would <a href=\\\"http://blog.airpapr.com/en/contact\\\">love to here from you</a>! Also, if you found any bugs or have any problems with airpapr, it would be great if you could drop a short <a href=\\\"https://github.com/airpapr/airpapr/issues\\\">issue report</a> on our github page.</p>\n<p>As you may also have noticed, we have decided to drop the German language support from the airpapr website. It was just not reasonable to take the extra time to translate every article into German, for a very small audience. Inserted we are focusing on writing the documentation of airpapr and the production of tutorials.</p></p>\n','','','airpapr-beta-release-0.png','','',1),
	(75,'news',1,1,0,'dev-update-airpapr-search-function','cat_name_show_en','cat_description_en','dev-update-airpapr-search-function','airpapr update: search function','26.03.11','Patrick','airpapr update: search function','<p>Welcome back to another airpapr development update. We are busy at work preparing airpapr for the beta release. Today we would like to show you a new feature we added to airpapr: The search function. Airpapr now has a built in search function which can be used in airpapr templates to give users the ability to search for any information in the articles posted. The search function also has a auto-suggestion function, which displays results as you are typing the search term, which makes searching even faster.</p>\r\n<p>Also we rebuilt the page navigation system. As a template designer you can choose the kind of navigation system you would like to use, e.g. links with &ldquo;older article&rdquo; or &ldquo;newer article&rdquo; text, a list of all pages (1, ,2 ,3, etc.) or just an empty &lt;a&gt; tag if you want to use just some images as links. At the moment we are writing a setup script for airpapr so that you can easily install airpapr on your web server. We are also hard at work writing the template API documentation, so that as soon as airpapr is released, you can start building your own templates with airpapr.</p>','<p>Welcome back to another airpapr development update. We are busy at work preparing airpapr for the beta release. Today we would like to show you a new feature we added to airpapr: The search function. Airpapr now has a built in search function which can be used in airpapr templates to give users the ability to search for any information in the articles posted. The search function also has a auto-suggestion function, which displays results as you are typing the search term, which makes searching even faster.</p>\n\n<p><p>Also we rebuilt the page navigation system. As a template designer you can choose the kind of navigation system you would like to use, e.g. links with &ldquo;older article&rdquo; or &ldquo;newer article&rdquo; text, a list of all pages (1, ,2 ,3, etc.) or just an empty &lt;a&gt; tag if you want to use just some images as links. At the moment we are writing a setup script for airpapr so that you can easily install airpapr on your web server. We are also hard at work writing the template API documentation, so that as soon as airpapr is released, you can start building your own templates with airpapr.</p></p>\n','','','dev-update-airpapr-search-function-0.png','','',1),
	(81,'',2,2,0,'download','cat_name_show_en','cat_description_en','download','download','25.04.11','Patrick','download','<p>airpapr is still in beta status at the moment. This means that airpapr still isn\\\'t quite finished yet, and you may encounter some unexpected bugs and errors while using airpapr. Still, airpaps is already stable enough to be used for smaller websites. If you are using airpapr,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://blog.airpapr.com/en/contact\\\">please give us feedback</a>!</p>\r\n<p>If you notice any bugs or errors while using airpapr, please <a href=\\\"https://github.com/airpapr/airpapr/issues\\\">check the issue page</a>, and if your problem has not yet been reported, please leave an bug report.</p>\r\n<p>You can download the latest airpapr build on our github page. Just click the \\\"download\\\" button on the upper right side of the page to get the latest version of airpapr. Before downloading, we recommend to read the <a href=\\\"http://blog.airpapr.com/en/page/documentation\\\">documentation</a>.</p>\r\n<h3><em><a href=\\\"https://github.com/airpapr/airpapr\\\">Download the latest airpapr build</a></em></h3>','<p>airpapr is still in beta status at the moment. This means that airpapr still isn\\\'t quite finished yet, and you may encounter some unexpected bugs and errors while using airpapr. Still, airpaps is already stable enough to be used for smaller websites. If you are using airpapr,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://blog.airpapr.com/en/contact\\\">please give us feedback</a>!</p>\n\n<p><p>If you notice any bugs or errors while using airpapr, please <a href=\\\"https://github.com/airpapr/airpapr/issues\\\">check the issue page</a>, and if your problem has not yet been reported, please leave an bug report.</p>\n<p>You can download the latest airpapr build on our github page. Just click the &#92;\"download&#92;\" button on the upper right side of the page to get the latest version of airpapr. Before downloading, we recommend to read the <a href=\\\"http://b